## Decisions Made
- Parallelize PR-level subagent execution in batch-refine: Each PR pipeline is independent (own context window, no shared state), so concurrent Agent tool calls in a single message is safe and eliminates linear time scaling.
- Keep intra-PR stages sequential: collect -> extract -> quality-gate has data dependencies within a single PR, so parallelizing within a PR is not feasible.

