- Agent tool parallelism requires all spawn calls in a single message: Claude Code launches subagents concurrently only when multiple Agent tool calls appear in one response.
- Intra-PR pipeline must remain sequential: Evidence Bundle feeds extract-candidates, which feeds quality-gate — data dependency chain.

